### Installation

## If Makefile already generated:
make maintainer-clean

## If Makefile is not yet generated, do:
: autoreconf -fi
: ./configure
: make maintainer-clean

## Edit to change the version:
: configure.ac
: README.md
: CHANGELOG

autoreconf -fi

./configure

make

## Recommended:
make check

## With elevated permissions if required:
sudo make install

## In order to uninstall, might require elevated permission:
: make uninstall

